          "name": "Please upload one valid ID. Supported IDs include UMID, National ID, SSS, TIN, Passport, Driver’s License, Postal ID, Voter ID, or Health Card",
          "fill": "#999999ff",
          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
          "width": 289,
          "content": "Please upload one valid ID. Supported IDs include UMID, National ID, SSS, TIN, Passport, Driver’s License, Postal ID, Voter ID, or Health Card",
          "lineHeight": 1.2857142857142858,
          "fontFamily": "PingFang SC",
          "fontSize": 14,
          "fontWeight": "normal"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "JvfxH",
          "x": 55,
          "y": 476,
          "name": "1. Please make sure that the ID card you upload is genuine and valid. 2. Please make sure that the uploaded ID card photo is clear and complete, otherwise it will not pass verification.",
