          "name": "Terms Of The Loans",
          "fill": "#ffffffff",
          "content": "Terms Of The Loans",
          "lineHeight": 1.2,
          "textAlignVertical": "bottom",
          "fontFamily": "PingFang SC",
          "fontSize": 20,
          "fontWeight": "normal"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "zVfMi",
          "x": 34,
          "y": 154,
          "name": "Maximum Annual Percentage Rate: 32.8%. For example, for a loan with a term of 90 days (3 months) and a total amount of 10,000 Rupees, after deducting a service fee of 100 Rupees (including credit scoring system fees, account fees, and third-party fees), the actual disbursed amount is 9,900 Rupees.",
          "fill": "#565656ff",
          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
          "width": 315,
          "content": "Maximum Annual Percentage Rate: 32.8%.\r\nFor example, for a loan with a term of 90 days (3 months) and a total amount of 10,000 Rupees, after deducting a service fee of 100 Rupees (including credit scoring system fees, account fees, and third-party fees), the actual disbursed amount is 9,900 Rupees.",
          "lineHeight": 1.4285714285714286,
          "fontFamily": "PingFang SC",
          "fontSize": 14,
          "fontWeight": "normal"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "wnFVs",
          "x": 34,
          "y": 384,
          "name": "We offer the following loan services: Loan Amount: Up to 50,000 Rupees. Loan Term: 90 days to 360 days. Service Fee: 100-400 Rupees. Daily Interest Rate: 0.08%. Maximum Annual Percentage Rate: 32.8%. For example, for a loan with a term of 90 days (3 months) and a total amount of 10,000 Rupees,",
          "fill": "#565656ff",
          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
          "width": 315,
          "content": "We offer the following loan services:\r\nLoan Amount: Up to 50,000 Rupees.\r\nLoan Term: 90 days to 360 days.\r\nService Fee: 100-400 Rupees.\r\nDaily Interest Rate: 0.08%.\r\nMaximum Annual Percentage Rate: 32.8%.\r\nFor example, for a loan with a term of 90 days (3 months) and a total amount of 10,000 Rupees, ",
          "lineHeight": 1.4285714285714286,
          "fontFamily": "PingFang SC",
